259
00:16:51,539 --> 00:16:53,172
IF THAT'S REALLY
HOW YOU FEEL,

260
00:16:59,205 --> 00:17:02,272
THEN YOU SHOULD SURRENDER
TO THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

261
00:17:03,905 --> 00:17:06,372
