I DID NOT KILL THE OLD MAN.

289
00:18:44,739 --> 00:18:46,439
BUT IF YOU REALLY WANT
TO SHOOT ME,

290
00:18:49,605 --> 00:18:51,572
GO AHEAD, SHOOT!

291
00:18:55,672 --> 00:18:57,039
SHOOT!

292
00:19:00,339 --> 00:19:03,139
